_sText:
My mission with this map was to make a gun-game map that actually looked decent, as far as visuals and game-play, due to the fact that most gun-game maps are visually bland, or the game-play/feel of the map is poor. This map is my attempt to having a visually appealing map and have great game-play.

If you see any bugs and/or suggestions, please feel free to comment below, all informative feedback is appreciated!
